

# install mozc

##1 install bazel

follow this guide https://bazel.build/install/compile-source#bootstrap-unix-prereq
  
##2 compile mozc using this guide https://fcitx-im.org/wiki/Compiling_Mozc


./bazel build -c opt --copt=-fPIC --config oss_linux \
            unix/fcitx5:fcitx5-mozc.so \
            server:mozc_server \
            gui/tool:mozc_tool


install using ../scripts/install_fcitx5_bazel and ../scripts/install_server_bazel 

  
